| Sl.No | Functions | Specifications |
|--|--|--|
| 1 | Stick rotations | The drumsticks should rotate from 0' to 45' at regular intervals. |
| 2 | Option Display | Displaying the 2 types of tunes |
| 3 | Tune Selection | Take one input at a time from the user for selecting the input. |
| 4 | Expected Repetitions| Displaying 2 or 4 as of options for selecting the number of repetitions. |
| 5 | Repetition selection | Playing the selected tune for ' 2 or 4 ' repetitions as per the input given by the user |
| 6 | Indicate process completion | Blinking LED's |
